why_it_failed: All attempts fell short because they focused solely on pre-filtering dimension tables into CTEs—a strategy that provides diminishing returns. The core bottleneck remains untouched: the massive join between catalog_sales and inventory with a non‑equi condition (inv_quantity_on_hand < cs_quantity), which generates a huge intermediate result before filtering. Additionally, the self‑join pattern on date_dim (d1, d2, d3) was not optimized; each attempt joined them independently, missing opportunities
